3736//
3737// IMPLEMENTATION SECTION
3738//
3739
3740#ifdef GLAD_IMPLEMENTATION
3741
3742#include <stdio.h>
3743#include <stdlib.h>
3744#include <string.h>
3745
3746struct gladGLversionStruct GLVersion;
3747
3748#if defined(GL_ES_VERSION_3_0) || defined(GL_VERSION_3_0)
3749#define _GLAD_IS_SOME_NEW_VERSION 1
3750#endif
3751
3752static int max_loaded_major;
3753static int max_loaded_minor;
3754
3755static const char *exts = NULL;
3756static int num_exts_i = 0;
3757static const char **exts_i = NULL;
3758
3759static int get_exts(void) {
3760#ifdef _GLAD_IS_SOME_NEW_VERSION
3761 if(max_loaded_major < 3) {
3762#endif
3763 exts = (const char *)glGetString(GL_EXTENSIONS);
3764#ifdef _GLAD_IS_SOME_NEW_VERSION
3765 } else {
3766 int index;
3767
3768 num_exts_i = 0;
3769 glGetIntegerv(GL_NUM_EXTENSIONS, &num_exts_i);
3770 if (num_exts_i > 0) {
3771 exts_i = (const char **)GLAD_REALLOC((void *)exts_i, num_exts_i * sizeof *exts_i);
3772 }
3773
3774 if (exts_i == NULL) {
3775 return 0;
3776 }
3777
3778 for(index = 0; index < num_exts_i; index++) {
3779 exts_i[index] = (const char*)glGetStringi(GL_EXTENSIONS, index);
3780 }
3781 }
3782#endif
3783 return 1;
3784}
3785
3786static void free_exts(void) {
3787 if (exts_i != NULL) {
3788 GLAD_FREE((char **)exts_i);
3789 exts_i = NULL;
3790 }
3791}
3792
3793static int has_ext(const char *ext) {
3794#ifdef _GLAD_IS_SOME_NEW_VERSION
3795 if(max_loaded_major < 3) {
3796#endif
3797 const char *extensions;
3798 const char *loc;
3799 const char *terminator;
3800 extensions = exts;
3801 if(extensions == NULL || ext == NULL) {
3802 return 0;
3803 }
3804
3805 while(1) {
3806 loc = strstr(extensions, ext);
3807 if(loc == NULL) {
3808 return 0;
3809 }
3810
3811 terminator = loc + strlen(ext);
3812 if((loc == extensions || *(loc - 1) == ' ') &&
3813 (*terminator == ' ' || *terminator == '\0')) {
3814 return 1;
3815 }
3816 extensions = terminator;
3817 }
3818#ifdef _GLAD_IS_SOME_NEW_VERSION
3819 } else {
3820 int index;
3821
3822 for(index = 0; index < num_exts_i; index++) {
3823 const char *e = exts_i[index];
3824
3825 if(strcmp(e, ext) == 0) {
3826 return 1;
3827 }
3828 }
3829 }
3830#endif
3831
3832 return 0;
3833}

3842int GLAD_GL_VERSION_3_0;

5366
5367static void find_coreGL(void) {
5368
5369 /* Thank you @elmindreda
5370 * https://github.com/elmindreda/greg/blob/master/templates/greg.c.in#L176
5371 * https://github.com/glfw/glfw/blob/master/src/context.c#L36
5372 */
5373 int i, major, minor;
5374
5375 const char* version;
5376 const char* prefixes[] = {
5377 "OpenGL ES-CM ",
5378 "OpenGL ES-CL ",
5379 "OpenGL ES ",
5380 NULL
5381 };
5382
5383 version = (const char*) glGetString(GL_VERSION);
5384 if (!version) return;
5385
5386 for (i = 0; prefixes[i]; i++) {
5387 const size_t length = strlen(prefixes[i]);
5388 if (strncmp(version, prefixes[i], length) == 0) {
5389 version += length;
5390 break;
5391 }
5392 }
5393
5394/* PR #18 */
5395#ifdef _MSC_VER
5396 sscanf_s(version, "%d.%d", &major, &minor);
5397#else
5398 sscanf(version, "%d.%d", &major, &minor);
5399#endif
5400
5401 GLVersion.major = major; GLVersion.minor = minor;
5402 max_loaded_major = major; max_loaded_minor = minor;
5403 GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_0 = (major == 1 && minor >= 0) || major > 1;
5404 GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_1 = (major == 1 && minor >= 1) || major > 1;
5405 GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_2 = (major == 1 && minor >= 2) || major > 1;
5406 GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_3 = (major == 1 && minor >= 3) || major > 1;
5407 GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_4 = (major == 1 && minor >= 4) || major > 1;
5408 GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_5 = (major == 1 && minor >= 5) || major > 1;
5409 GLAD_GL_VERSION_2_0 = (major == 2 && minor >= 0) || major > 2;
5410 GLAD_GL_VERSION_2_1 = (major == 2 && minor >= 1) || major > 2;
5411 GLAD_GL_VERSION_3_0 = (major == 3 && minor >= 0) || major > 3;
5412 GLAD_GL_VERSION_3_1 = (major == 3 && minor >= 1) || major > 3;
5413 GLAD_GL_VERSION_3_2 = (major == 3 && minor >= 2) || major > 3;
5414 GLAD_GL_VERSION_3_3 = (major == 3 && minor >= 3) || major > 3;
5415 if (GLVersion.major > 3 || (GLVersion.major >= 3 && GLVersion.minor >= 3)) {
5416 max_loaded_major = 3;
5417 max_loaded_minor = 3;
5418 }
5419}
5420
5421int gladLoadGLLoader(GLADloadproc load) {
5422 GLVersion.major = 0; GLVersion.minor = 0;
5423 glGetString = (PFNGLGETSTRINGPROC)load("glGetString");
5424 if(glGetString == NULL) return 0;
5425 if(glGetString(GL_VERSION) == NULL) return 0;
5426 find_coreGL();
5427 load_GL_VERSION_1_0(load);
5428 load_GL_VERSION_1_1(load);
5429 load_GL_VERSION_1_2(load);
5430 load_GL_VERSION_1_3(load);
5431 load_GL_VERSION_1_4(load);
5432 load_GL_VERSION_1_5(load);
5433 load_GL_VERSION_2_0(load);
5434 load_GL_VERSION_2_1(load);
5435 load_GL_VERSION_3_0(load);
5436 load_GL_VERSION_3_1(load);
5437 load_GL_VERSION_3_2(load);
5438 load_GL_VERSION_3_3(load);
5439
5440 if (!find_extensionsGL()) return 0;
5441 load_GL_AMD_debug_output(load);
5442 load_GL_ARB_ES2_compatibility(load);
5443 load_GL_ARB_buffer_storage(load);
5444 load_GL_ARB_debug_output(load);
5445 load_GL_ARB_draw_buffers(load);
5446 load_GL_ARB_draw_buffers_blend(load);
5447 load_GL_ARB_fragment_program(load);
5448 load_GL_ARB_framebuffer_object(load);
5449 load_GL_ARB_multisample(load);
5450 load_GL_ARB_sample_locations(load);
5451 load_GL_ARB_texture_compression(load);
5452 load_GL_ARB_texture_multisample(load);
5453 load_GL_ARB_uniform_buffer_object(load);
5454 load_GL_ARB_vertex_array_object(load);
5455 load_GL_ARB_vertex_attrib_binding(load);
5456 load_GL_ARB_vertex_buffer_object(load);
5457 load_GL_ARB_vertex_program(load);
5458 load_GL_ARB_vertex_shader(load);
5459 load_GL_ATI_element_array(load);
5460 load_GL_ATI_fragment_shader(load);
5461 load_GL_ATI_vertex_array_object(load);
5462 load_GL_EXT_blend_color(load);
5463 load_GL_EXT_blend_equation_separate(load);
5464 load_GL_EXT_blend_func_separate(load);

5468 load_GL_EXT_framebuffer_object(load);
5469 load_GL_EXT_vertex_array(load);
5470 load_GL_EXT_vertex_shader(load);
5471 return GLVersion.major != 0 || GLVersion.minor != 0;
